OL,3,CWhisky distilleries celebrate Trump's
OL,4,Cremoval of tariffs
OL,6,FDistilleries in the South of Scotland
OL,7,Fare celebrating after US President
OL,8,FDonald Trump announced that tariffs
OL,9,Fwould be lifted on imports of Scotch
OL,10,FWhisky to the country.
OL,12,FPresident Trump made the declaration
OL,13,Ffollowing King Charles and Queen
OL,14,FCamilla's state visit to the US.
OL,16,FBosses at the Scotch Whisky
OL,17,FAssociation (SWA) in Scotland said it
OL,18,Fwould be a "significant boost" for the
OL,19,Findustry in what they say is their
OL,20,Fmost valuable export market.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
