OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1777896668
OL,3,CWhisky distilleries celebrate Trump's
OL,4,Cremoval of tariffs
OL,6,FWhile those at Annandale Distillery,
OL,7,Fthe largest manufacturer of Scotch
OL,8,FWhisky in the South of Scotland,
OL,9,Fdescribed it as "transformative".
OL,11,FThe King and Queen finished their four-
OL,12,Fday state visit to the US on Thursday,
OL,13,Fwhere they visited Washington DC, New
OL,14,FYork and Virginia.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
