CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1777896668
OL,3,CWhisky distilleries celebrate Trump's
OL,4,Cremoval of tariffs
OL,6,FIn a post on his Truth Social account,
OL,7,FTrump said, "In Honor of the King and
OL,8,FQueen of the United Kingdom, who have
OL,9,Fjust left the White House, soon headed
OL,10,Fback to their wonderful Country, I
OL,11,Fwill be removing the Tariffs and
OL,12,FRestrictions on Whiskey having to do
OL,13,Fwith Scotland's ability to work with
OL,14,Fthe Commonwealth of Kentucky on
OL,15,FWhiskey and Bourbon."
OL,17,FHe added, "The King and Queen got me
OL,18,Fto do something nobody else was able
OL,19,Fto do, without hardly even asking!"
OL,26,@oD@MOUyD@KOU{D@cO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
