PN,35504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1777896668
OL,3,CWhisky distilleries celebrate Trump's
OL,4,Cremoval of tariffs
OL,6,FThe US had imposed a 10% baseline
OL,7,Ftariff on imports of most British
OL,8,Fgoods, including Scotch Whisky, last
OL,9,Fyear.
OL,11,FSpeaking after learning that tariffs
OL,12,Fwould be lifted, spokesperson for
OL,13,FAnnandale Distilleries, Lee Medd,
OL,14,Fsaid, ""This trade victory is a
OL,15,Ftransformative moment for Annandale.
OL,17,F"For too long, the 'tariff yo-yo'
OL,18,Fcreated uncertainty that hindered long-
OL,19,Fterm investment in the States. Now, we
OL,20,Faren't just dipping a toe in the
OL,21,Fwater; we are diving in.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1777896668
OL,3,CWhisky distilleries celebrate Trump's
OL,4,Cremoval of tariffs
OL,6,F"By achieving price parity, we are
OL,7,Fmaking our rare Single Cask spirits
OL,8,Faccessible to the American market in a
OL,9,Fway that feels fair and transparent.
OL,11,FWe are thrilled to finally bridge the
OL,12,Fgap between Annan and the US, allowing
OL,13,Fus to share our story and our spirit
OL,14,Fwithout the burden of unnecessary
OL,15,Ftrade barriers."
OL,17,FThe SWA had estimated that estimated
OL,18,Fthat the tariffs were costing the
OL,19,Fsector #4m a week.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
