OL,3,CWhisky distilleries celebrate Trump's
OL,4,Cremoval of tariffs
OL,6,FUK business and trade secretary Peter
OL,7,FKyle said: "This is great news for our
OL,8,Fscotch whisky industry, which is worth
OL,9,Falmost #1bn in exports and supports
OL,10,Fthousands of jobs across the UK."
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
